---
title: Homepage
---

<%= partial 'header', locals: { home: true } %>

<div class="header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="logo logo-sm">partial :: Conf -> 2018</h1>
    <h2>30 November 2018, Sofia</h2>

    <p>
      The web, lambda calculus, the meaning of life and everything else.
      Distribute yourself with some Erlang. Prevent you some runtime errors
      with Elm. Transactional memorize yourself with some Clojure… 
    </p>

    <a href="https://goo.gl/PpcTAS" class="btn-default btn-invert">Become a speaker</a>
    <a href="blog/announcement-v2-0" class="btn-default btn-invert">Read the announcement</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="spacing-both" id="cfp">
  <div class="container accent-container">
    <div class="accent">
      <%= image_tag 'library_accent.png' %>
    </div>
    <div class="spotlight accent-cointainer">
      <div class="col">
        <h3>Call for Papers</h3>

        <p>
          We are looking for talks about modern functional programming
          languages and technologies for the web. The timeslot is 20 to 30
          minutes.
        </p>

        <p>
          We would love to hear from your experience on how they are used in
          your company, or personal projects. Here are the usual suspects:
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li>Erlang, Elixir</li>
          <li>Clojure, ClojureScript</li>
          <li>Elm, PureScript, Haskell</li>
          <li>React, Redux</li>
          <li>Everything λ</li>
        </ul>

        <p>The deadline is 20th of August.</p>

        <div class="btn-wrapper">
          <a href="https://goo.gl/PpcTAS" class="btn-primary" target="_blank">Submit your talk</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="light spacing-both">
  <div class="container text">
    <h2>Subscribe for News</h2>

    <p>
      The tickets will be out soon. Subscribe to our newsletter to be the first
      to learn about them. Your email won't be shared with partners or any
      other third party.
    </p>

    <div class="mailchimp">
      <div id="mc_embed_signup">
        <form action="//partialconf.us15.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=956b02b076ff39618af330bb0&amp;id=6e539c98fc" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" class="validate" target="_blank" novalidate>
          <div id="mc_embed_signup_scroll">
            <input type="email" value="" name="EMAIL" class="email" id="mce-EMAIL" placeholder="your@email.com" required>
            <div class="hide"><input type="text" name="b_956b02b076ff39618af330bb0_6e539c98fc" tabindex="-1" value=""></div>
            <button class="btn-primary btn-invert" type="submit" value="Subscribe" name="subscribe">Subscribe</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="spacing-both">
  <div class="container accent-container">
    <h2>Our partners</h2>

    <div class='index-sponsors-section'>
      <% data.sponsors.each do |meta| %>
        <% meta.sponsors.each do |sponsor| %>
          <span class="sponsor-avatar">
            <%= link_to image_tag(sponsor.logo), "/partners##{sponsor.id}" %>
          </span>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%= partial 'footer' %>
